summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2013 RAM 1500. WHILE DRIVING VARIOUS SPEEDS AND WHILE THE VEHICLE WAS STATIONARY, WATER LEAKED INTO THE REAR CABIN OF THE VEHICLE. SUNSET CHRYSLER OF GRENADA, MISSISSIPPI COULD NOT DIAGNOSE THE SOURCE OF THE WATER ENTRY, BUT STATED THAT THE WATER MAY HAVE COME FROM A LOOSE LIGHT FIXTURE IN THE VEHICLE. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE ISSUE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 110,000. THE VIN WAS NOT AVAILABLE.
